lyrics:
dream dream dream surfer, hasta la vista surfista robot

big waves, big waves, oh yes

I close my eyes, the world fades away
In the realm of dreams, I'm here to stay 
Floating high, on angel's wings I soar
Through the vast cosmos, to the distant shores (ooh-ooh)


Dream dream dream, let the colors beam (ooh-yeah)
In the land of make-believe, where anything's extreme
Hasta la vista, robot, we're breaking free (ooh-ooh)
In this fantasy, our hearts sing in harmony (ooh-yeah)
